U.S. September Truck Stop Credit Card Swipes Fell

-- B y   K r i s t y   S c h e u b l e
-- 
2011-10-12T13:00:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-12/u-s-september-truck-stop-credit-card-swipes-fell-table-.html
Credit card swipes for purchases of
 diesel fuel  at truck stops across the U.S. declined last month,
according to the Ceridian-UCLA Pulse of Commerce Index.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kristy Scheuble in Washington at   kmckeaney@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
